{ While these principles are useful, understand that they precede concrete calculations. For example, it is perfectly alright to move the f-pawn if your King is still safe and well taken care of by your other pieces.   With that, we shall put them to practice with the next section, 'Dubious or Not?'. Check out the introduction to the next chapter for more details! }
