{ g6 is a good anchor to open the h-file, but it generally effective only if Black has castled. }
5... c6 6. h5
{ White's exchange sacrifice is not good if Black hasn't castled. } 6... Nxh5
7. Rxh5 gxh5 8. Qxh5
{ White might enjoy better activity, but as long as Black doesn't castle, White will struggle to find a decent concrete plan. Overall, White's play is OFF BEAT or even DUBIOUS while Black's play was PERFECT. }
*

