[SetUp "1"]

{ What if Black had taken on f6 with the Queen instead ? Does the e-file still hold the same value as a strategical target? }
12. Nxd5
{ We certainly would not mind sacrificing a piece for two pawns to expose Black's King.   12.Bxd5  This move similarly works, but it does not force exd5 since the Bishop isn't threatening anything on d5.  12...exd5?  13.Nxd5 }
12... exd5 13. Rhe1+ Kf8 14. Bxd5
{ White is significantly more active than Black and is not even down that much material. }
*

