{ Threatening a discovered check on the King   9.Qd4  c5  c5 is less effective because White has the c3 Knight developed. This means White can castle Queenside pretty quickly.  10.Nxd7+  Ke7  11.Qe5+  Kxd7  12.Bf4  White is only one move away from castling long, giving Black no time to fend the attack off. }
