{ Black defended c6 with ...Bd7. How do we continue the attack ? } 17. Rxd7
{ Removing the key defender of the light squares. c6 will surely fall now. }
17... Nxd7 18. Bxc6
{ White can win yet another piece for the sacrificed material. } *

