14. d5
{ Opening the d-file while chasing the c6 Bishop away from the a4-e8 diagonal. }
14... exd5 15. exd5 Bxd5 16. Bb5
{ Now White has both the d-file and the a4-e8 diagonal. Also, the e-file is yet another exploitable weakness. }
