18. Qg4
{ Skewering g6 and g7. Black does not have time to castle. Instead, he must defend everything with ...Kf7.   18.e4?!  Not forcing enough. Black can return one pawn and quickly castle.  18...Bf7  19.exd5  O-O  20.dxc6  Nxc6  Comparatively speaking, Black manages to get a decent position. His King is safe and his pieces are not too passive. }
18... Kf7 19. h5
{ Binding Black on the light squares before opening up the position. } *

